{"word":"χαλκός","slug":"χαλκός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>χαλϰός, οῦ, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ orig.\">orig.</a> unclear]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘metal (copper, brass, or bronze) as material for a manufactured commodity’, <b>metal <a href='B:730 18:12'>Rv 18:12</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘an object made of metal’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> that produces a resounding tone <b>(brass) gong <a href='B:530 13:1'>1 Cor 13:1</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> money <b><a href='B:470 10:9'>Mt 10:9</a>; <a href='B:480 6:8'>Mk 6:8</a>; <a href='B:480 12:41'>12:41</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:χαλκολίβανον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:χαλκοῦς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}